《南方公园》的创作人没有直接回应喜剧中心取消重播该集的决定，据报导说这是因为他们被要求避免谈及这起事件，以免使汤姆·克鲁斯尴尬<ref name="nypost_2006-03-17"/>。但他们于3月17日在《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》杂志发表了一份声份，署名为“特雷·帕克和马特·斯通，魔王茲努的仆人”<ref name="varietystatement">{{Citenews|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117939918?categoryid=14&cs=1|title=Inside Move: 'South Park' feeling some celeb heat?|website=variety.com|accessdate=2006-11-04|language=en|archive-date=2012-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120422192038/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117939918?categoryid=14&cs=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》把“困在衣柜里”重播引起的争议形容为“衣柜门”事件<ref>{{Citenews|last=Collins|first=Scott|title=CHANNEL ISLAND; Clamor outside 'South Park' closet; 'Mission: Impossible' studio joins Cruise's camp in denying it strong-armed scrapping of Scientology repeat.|work=《洛杉矶时报》|pages=Calendar Desk; Part E; Pg. 16|date=2006-03-18|language=en}}</ref>。《[[独立报|独立报]]》后来引用《洛杉矶时报》，指争议已为《南方公园》的创作人产生正面的公众形象：“对于斯通和帕克来说，衣柜门事件将会是一份源源不绝的礼物。”<ref>{{Citenews|last=Usborne|first=David|title=''South Park'' declares war on Tom Cruise; Cartoon's parody of Scientology is taken off air, prompting accusations of censorship.|work=《独立报》|pages=NEWS; Pg. 44|date=2006-03-19|language=en|url=http://news.independent.co.uk/media/article352197.ece|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070224043328/http://news.independent.co.uk/media/article352197.ece|archivedate=2007-02-24|accessdate=2008-04-12}}</ref>自此，“衣柜门”便被其他媒体如《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》用来指代艾萨克·海斯的离去和该集重播引起的“骚动”。<ref name="emerson">{{Citenews|last=Emerson|first=Jim|title=Closetgate: Latest shocking updates!|work=《芝加哥太阳报》|date=2006-03-20|language=en|url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20060320/SCANNERS/60320007|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090830035115/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20060320%2FSCANNERS%2F60320007|archivedate=2009-08-30|accessdate=2017-06-08}}</ref>

汤姆·克鲁斯的发言人在争议发生后不久作出回应，并对[[美联社|美联社]]说关于汤姆·克鲁斯参与事件的传言“并不真实”，“他并没有那样说”<ref>{{Citenews|last=Carlson|first=Erin|title='South Park'-Scientology battle rages|work=美联社|date=2006-03-17|language=en|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2006-03-17-south-park-scientology_x.htm|accessdate=2008-03-13|archive-date=2008-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080328010457/http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2006-03-17-south-park-scientology_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据《华盛顿邮报》，汤姆·克鲁斯的公关人员指出：“汤姆与这起事件毫无关联。过去六个月他一直在为《谍中谍3》进行宣传。我们不知道这从何而来。”<ref name="wapo_2006-03-18"/>汤姆·克鲁斯本人在4月中旬接受[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]《[[黄金时段_(电视节目)|黄金时段]]》节目专访时就事件作出回应，当他被问到他有没有参与阻止喜剧中心重播“困在衣柜里”，他说：“首先，你可以想像与任何一个人一同坐下进行讨论吗？我决不会与人坐下并质疑他们的信仰。这是事实：我甚至不准备把它形容为高尚。我真的不知道这件事。我在工作、拍摄电影；我有我的家庭。我很忙。我不会用我的时间问‘人们怎样说我？’”<ref>{{Citenews|url=http://www.hollywood.com/news/Cruise_No_Oprah_Regrets/3491532|title=Cruise: 'No Oprah Regrets'|publisher=hollywood.com|date=2006-04-16|language=en|accessdate=2007-06-16|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120915190646/http://www.hollywood.com/news/Cruise_No_Oprah_Regrets/3491532|archivedate=2012-09-15|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

2006年4月，《电视周刊》报导《南方公园》的支持者已在互联网上的多个站点发布该集。<ref name="hibberd">{{Citenews|last=Hibberd|first=James|title='South Park' Episode Lives; Scientology Story Line Thrives Online as Comedy Central Looks the Other Way|work=《电视周刊》|pages=TV Currents|date=2006-04-03|language=en}}</ref>当时，该集在影片分享网站[[YouTube|YouTube]]的观看次数已超过70万次，支持该集重播的一个签名活动则已获得5,000个签名。<ref name="hibberd" />《电视周刊》指喜剧中心“对‘困在衣柜里’在网上的扩散有不同的看法”。<ref name="hibberd" />拥有喜剧中心的[[MTV网络|MTV网络]]的一名发言人证实他们并没有要求YouTube网站删除该集的影片。<ref name="hibberd" />《形势室》节目也指喜剧中心的网站上仍有该集的影片。<ref name="blitzer">{{Citenews | last =Blitzer | first =Wolf | coauthors =Chris Lawrence, Abbi Tatton | title =Fourth Year of War in Iraq Begins; Could Democrats Launch Impeachment Campaign Against Bush? | work =《形势室》 | publisher =有线电视新闻网 | date =2006-03-20 | language =en | url =http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0603/20/sitroom.03.html | accessdate =2007-11-06 | archive-date =2012-07-23 | archive-url =https://archive.is/20120723/http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0603/20/sitroom.03.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>2006年5月，“困在衣柜里”在[[伦敦|伦敦]]的[[国家电影剧院|国家电影剧院]]免费放映，剧集完结后有一段帕克和斯通的讨论，他们说这次放映是“言论自由的显示”。<ref name="ninemsnstaff">{{Citenews |1= |title=Cruise loses 'South Park' battle |work=National Nine News |publisher=1997- 2007 ninemsn Pty Ltd |date=2006-05-18 |language=en |url=http://news.ninemsn.com.au/article.aspx?id=102210 |accessdate=2007-11-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070817035719/http://news.ninemsn.com.au/article.aspx?id=102210 |archivedate=2007-08-17 }}</ref>

2006年7月19日，喜剧中心频道在[[太平洋时间|太平洋时间]]10:00重播该集<ref name="timgoodman" /><ref>{{Citenews|url=http://tv.ign.com/articles/718/718226p1.html|title=South Park "Trapped in the Closet" Episode to Air Again|publisher=tv.ign.com|accessdate=2006-11-04|language=en|archive-date=2006-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060822093006/http://tv.ign.com/articles/718/718226p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[美国东部时间|东部时间]]7月23日23:00和9月24日22:00再次重播。斯通说：“如果他们不重播这集，我们会有大问题，我们也不会再与他们合作。”<ref>{{Citenews |coauthors=美联社 |title=‘South Park' Scientology episode set to rerun: Show that pokes fun at Tom Cruise was abruptly pulled back in March |work=MSNBC |publisher=NBC |date=2006-09-12 |language=en |url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/13834457/ |accessdate=2007-03-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071026102932/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/13834457/ |archivedate=2007-10-26 }}</ref>该集被安排重播后，帕克和斯通接受有线电视新闻网《好莱坞万花筒》专访，他们表示各种争议增加了该集的知名度。<ref name="showbiz06">{{Citenews | last = Hammer | first = A.J. | coauthors = Mary Murphy, TV Guide | title = Cruise and South Park; Princess Di Photos; Movie Reviews; Technology Addiction | work = 《好莱坞万花筒》 | language = en | publisher = 有线电视新闻网 | date = 2006-07-14 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0607/14/sbt.01.html | 10 =  | accessdate = 2008-04-12 | archive-date = 2007-11-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071124055629/http://edition.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0607/14/sbt.01.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>帕克说：“似乎宣传人员都不能为我们对此作出更好的安排。你知道这是什么意思吗？这似乎有点异常。我认为汤姆·克鲁斯为《南方公园》做的比世上任何一个人都多。”<ref name="showbiz06" />该集被包含在几套DVD系列之中，包括《{{lang|en|South Park the Hits: Volume 1}}》和《{{lang|en|South Park: The Complete Ninth Season}}》<ref>{{Citenews |title=Entertainment: More Naughty Fun |publisher=《休斯敦纪事报》|author=Westbrook, Bruce|date=2007-03-06|language=en|accessdate=2007-03-10 }}</ref>。虽然有指山达基教会或汤姆·克鲁斯曾要求该集不要以DVD的形式发布<ref name="timgoodman">{{Citenews |last=Goodman |first=Tim |title=Death March With Cocktails: 'South Park' at 10 trumps Tom Cruise |work=《旧金山纪事报》 |language=en |publisher=Hearst Communications Inc. |date=2006-07-15 |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2006/07/15/DDG6LJU24T1.DTL |accessdate=2007-10-20 |archive-date=2007-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012154152/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2006%2F07%2F15%2FDDG6LJU24T1.DTL |dead-url=no }}</ref>，喜剧中心的网站上至今仍有该集的影片<ref>{{Citenews |title=South Park TV Show Episode 912 Episode Trapped in the Closet |work=喜剧中心 |publisher=Comedy Central |url=http://southpark.comedycentral.com/video_by_episode.jhtml?episodeId=103804 |accessdate=2008-01-18 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080127235546/http://southpark.comedycentral.com/video_by_episode.jhtml?episodeId=103804 |archivedate=2008-01-27 }}</ref>。

