==反应==
在一篇评论《{{lang|en|South Park: The Complete Ninth Season}}》的文章中，《[[丹佛邮报|丹佛邮报]]》指出有关汤姆·克鲁斯的笑话得到“壮丽的呈现”，并认为“通过重覆的观看可发现其中的深度，就像节目大体上一样”。<ref>{{Citenews|last=Wenzel|first=John|title="South Park" becomes a gem|work=《丹佛邮报》|date=2007-03-19|url=http://www.denverpost.com/entertainment/ci_5475880|accessdate=2007-10-20|language=en|archive-date=2007-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012115413/http://www.denverpost.com/entertainment/ci_5475880|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》则指斯通和帕克“可能因为取笑汤姆·克鲁斯和山达基教而达到了事业的高峰”。<ref name="timgoodman" />《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》的一篇文章指《南方公园》“差劲地讽刺”L·罗恩·哈巴德的文字。<ref>{{Citenews|title=Is Scientology dangerous? - As an historian compares a Tom Cruise PR video for Scientology to the work of Goebbels, Chris Ayres reports from LA: is the organisation a dangerous cult, or a harmless celebrity club?|work=《泰晤士报》|date=2008-01-23|language=en|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/comment/faith/article3232421.ece|accessdate=2008-01-23|archive-date=2008-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080511144917/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/comment/faith/article3232421.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===分析===
《美国宗教学会期刊》的一篇文章指该集是“对山达基教会苛刻的讽刺。”<ref>{{cite journal |last=Urban |first=Hugh B. |title=Fair Game: Secrecy, Security, and the Church of Scientology in Cold War America |url=https://academic.oup.com/jaar/article-abstract/74/2/356/764149 |journal=Journal of the American Academy of Religion |volume=74 |issue=2 |pages=356—389 |publisher=美国宗教学会 |date=2006-04-26 |id={{ISSN|1477-4585}}, {{ISSN|0002-7189}} |accessdate=2007-10-20 |archive-date=2018-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180211003922/https://academic.oup.com/jaar/article-abstract/74/2/356/764149 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[特拉华大学|特拉华大学]]哲学系教授[[理查德·汉利|理查德·汉利]]在著作《{{lang|en|South Park and Philosophy: Bigger, Longer, and More Penetrating}}》中分析山达基教的神话，<ref name="hanley">{{cite book|last=Hanley|first=Richard|title=''South Park and Philosophy: Bigger, Longer, and More Penetrating''|url=https://archive.org/details/southparkphiloso0000unse|publisher=Open Court|date=2007-03-28|pages=[https://archive.org/details/southparkphiloso0000unse/page/23 23], 24, 32, 41, 246, 247, 262, 283|isbn=0812696131}}</ref><ref name="greto">{{Citenews|last=Greto|first=Victor|title=I offend, therefore I am: University of Delaware professor aimed for 'rude and crude ' in his book on 'South Park'|work=The News Journal, Delaware Online|publisher=USA Today, Gannett|date=2007-04-02}}</ref>汉利说“困在衣柜里”中关于茲努的神话“完全荒谬”。他以山达基教的神话和基督教的童贞女生子和[[圣餐变体|圣餐变体]]比较，说“这些信仰与山达基教的神话根本一样荒谬”。<ref name="hanley" /><ref name="greto" />他继续对流行程度和传统在决定信仰“坚实性”的“证据力”作出哲学分析。<ref name="greto" />

[[西南明尼苏达州立大学|西南明尼苏达州立大学]]哲学系教授罗伯特·阿普也在著作《{{lang|en|South Park and Philosophy: You Know, I Learned Something Today}}》中对该集的哲学和文化观点作出分析，<ref name="arp">{{cite book|last=Arp|first=Robert (Editor)|coauthors=William Irwin (Series Editor)|title=South Park and Philosophy: You Know, I Learned Something Today|url=https://archive.org/details/southparkphiloso00arpr_339|publisher=Blackwell Publishing (The Blackwell Philosophy & Pop Culture Series)|date=2006-12-11|pages=[https://archive.org/details/southparkphiloso00arpr_339/page/n38 27], 59, 60, 118, 120, 132, 137, 138, 140, 224|id=ISBN 1405161604 , ISBN 978-1405161602}}</ref>并在书中的一节分析喜剧中心对该集的反应。<ref name="arp" />他提到“困在衣柜里”中使用的字幕──“山达基教徒真的相信这些”，指“[[关于摩门教|关于摩门教]]”一集也有使用同样方法。在提及相似的字幕使用时，他说相对于该集，喜剧中心的做法表现出做法的不协调。他解释：“整体来说，本集对山达基教远较‘关于摩门教’对摩门教仁慈。”<ref name="arp" />他又指喜剧中心曾表明不会重播该集，但2006年7月12日又宣布将会重播。<ref name="arp" />

===获奖===
《南方公园》的工作人员因为“困在衣柜里”获[[劳伦斯·沃勒斯海姆|劳伦斯·沃勒斯海姆]]创办的[[对抗高压手法网络|对抗高压手法网络]]组织选为“2005年对抗高压手法网络年度人物”。<ref>{{Citenews |last=Staff |title=FACTNet.org Names South Park TV Show Staff FACTNet Person(s) of the Year for 2005 for their Recent Scientology Tom Cruise John Travolta Episode |work=Fight Against Coercive Tactics Network |publisher=F.A.C.T.Net, Inc. |date=2005-11-20 |url=http://www.factnet.org/letters/FACTNewsNovember2005SouthPark.html |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071114161306/http://www.factnet.org/letters/FACTNewsNovember2005SouthPark.html |archivedate=2007-11-14 |accessdate=2008-04-12 }}</ref>罗伯特·阿普提到《南方公园》因为敢于对不宽容作出批评而在2006年4月获得[[皮博迪奖|皮博迪奖]]。<ref name="arp" />

《南方公园》的创作者把该集提交角逐[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]，但斯通承认“我们这样做就是要做浑蛋，对喜剧中心的一句‘去你的’。”<ref>{{Citenews | last = Schwatz | first = Missy | title = 'South' Rises Again | work = 《娱乐周刊》 | pages = 12 | publisher = Bell & Howell Information and Learning Company | date = 2006-07-28 | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1217338,00.html | accessdate = 2008-03-13 | language = en | archive-date = 2008-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081006004952/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1217338,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>令他们感到意外的是，该集在2006年7月6日获得艾美奖最佳一小时以下动画节目提名，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.emmys.org/downloads/images/2006emmys/PrimetimeNoms.php |title=58th Primetime Emmy Awards |publisher=emmys.org |accessdate=2006-11-04 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090715002753/http://www.emmys.org/downloads/images/2006emmys/PrimetimeNoms.php |archivedate=2009-07-15 }}</ref>这是《南方公园》第6次获得提名（其中2005年的“[[永远的好朋友|永远的好朋友]]”获奖）。<ref>{{Citenews |url=http://animatedtv.about.com/b/a/201869.htm |title="South Park" Finally Wins Emmy |publisher=animatedtv.about.com |accessdate=2006-11-04 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071013035953/http://animatedtv.about.com/b/a/201869.htm |archivedate=2007-10-13 }}</ref>《[[辛普森一家|辛普森一家]]》的“[[一个似乎永远讲不完的故事|一个似乎永远讲不完的故事]]”最终获得该奖项。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.emmys.org/media/releases/2006/crtvarts2006_rel.pdf |title=Create Arts Emmys winners |publisher=emmys.org |format=PDF |accessdate=2007-03-10 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060929122955/http://www.emmys.org/media/releases/2006/crtvarts2006_rel.pdf |archivedate=2006-09-29 }}</ref>《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的汤姆·奥尼尔认为后来2007年10月播放的“More Crap”一集出现的字幕“艾美奖获奖系列”是用来联系“困在衣柜里”失落的艾美奖。<ref>{{Citenews | last = O'Neil | first = Tom | title = Did 'South Park' dump on the Emmys? | work = 《洛杉矶时报》 | date = 2007-10-11 | url = http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2007/10/did-south-park-.html | accessdate = 2007-10-20 | language = en | archive-date = 2008-04-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080405194044/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2007/10/did-south-park-.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>该集被喜剧中心列为“10集改变世界的南方公园”之一，<ref>{{Citenews |url=http://www.newpaltz.edu/oracle/article.cfm?id=2563 |title=South Park: Crude and Rude as Ever |publisher=newpaltz.edu |accessdate=2006-11-10 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927182600/http://www.newpaltz.edu/oracle/article.cfm?id=2563 |archivedate=2007-09-27 }}</ref>这10集在2006年9月24日起重播。<ref>{{Citenews|title=Comedy Central to Air South Park Episodes That Changed the World|publisher=news.awn.com|date=2006-09-19|language=en}}</ref>

